734 A.2d 720 ATTORNEY GRIEVANCE COMMISSION OF MARYLAND, Petitioner, v. Jack Douglas LEONARD, Respondent. Misc. (Subtitle AG) No. 92,

Sept. Term, 1998.

Court of Appeals of Maryland. Aug. 9, 1999.

ORDER

ORDERED that the Respondent, Jack Douglas Leonard, II, be and he is hereby reprimanded for his violation of Rules 1.3 and 1.4 of the Maryland Rules of Professional Conduct.
